title: The service can read your private messages

tosdr.case: The service can read your private messages
tosdr.tldr: The privacy policy states that: 'Information we collect may include but not be limited to username, email address, and any messages, images, transient VOIP data (to enable communication delivery only) or other content you send via the chat feature.'

quoteText: Information we collect may include but not be limited to username, email address, and any messages, images, transient VOIP data (to enable communication delivery only) or other content you send via the chat feature.
